    A class representing the cards in the game Shape up.

    Deck
    A class representing the deck in the game Shape up.
    Fill
    An enumeration class defines the two fill (filled or hollow) of the card.

    A class representing the joueur in the game Shape up.
    Shape
    An enumeration class defines the three shapes (circle, triangle, square) of the card.
